data.description: Adorable, Ranch-Style Home w/ 3BD/2BTH, waiting for New Family to Call It Home! Tiled Foyer Leads to Open Floor Plan w/ Formal Dining, Large Living Room w/ Wood-burning Fireplace & Beautiful, Floor-to-Ceiling Stone Accent w/ Hearth. Upgraded Kitchen w/ SS Appls, White, Painted Cabinets, Tile Backsplash w/ Mosaic Accent Design, Built-in Pantry, Island w/ Room for 2, 18” Tile Floors, Breakfast Nook, & Direct Access to W/D Area! Spacious Master Offers Private Bth. 2 Other GST RMs w/ GST BTH & Flex RM Can be Used as Office, Gym, Mud RM, & More, Complete This Floor Plan. Exterior Features Incl. Large, Fenced-in Backyard w/ Patio, Playground, 10x10 Shed, Firepit, & Garden Box. HVAC Replaced (2015) & Serviced Annually. Roof Replaced (2016). New Windows (2022), New Garage Door Panel & Motor w/ Warranty (2023) & Pull-down Attic w/ Useable Storage Space. Conveniently Located Close to Ft. Liberty/Bragg, Medical Facilities, Schools, Shopping, Restaurants, & More. Make Appt To See Before It’s Gone!
